<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>SelectionTemplate_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>serves<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>foundational<sp/>base<sp/>for<sp/>defining<sp/>and<sp/>applying<sp/>event<sp/>selections<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework.<sp/>It<sp/>provides<sp/>robust<sp/>mechanisms<sp/>for<sp/>interpreting<sp/>data<sp/>from<sp/>ROOT<sp/>files,<sp/>managing<sp/>event<sp/>weights,<sp/>and<sp/>associating<sp/>metadata.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>is<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>inherited<sp/>by<sp/>specific<sp/>selection<sp/>implementations,<sp/>offering<sp/>common<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>data<sp/>processing<sp/>and<sp/>filtering,<sp/>with<sp/>a<sp/>strong<sp/>emphasis<sp/>on<sp/>performance<sp/>through<sp/>its<sp/>C++<sp/>backend.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>SelectionTemplate_class<sp/>The<sp/>SelectionTemplate<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>for<sp/>direct<sp/>and<sp/>optimized<sp/>interaction<sp/>with<sp/>C++<sp/>objects<sp/>and<sp/>types,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>crucial<sp/>for<sp/>efficient<sp/>processing<sp/>of<sp/>large<sp/>datasets<sp/>in<sp/>high-energy<sp/>physics.<sp/>It<sp/>encapsulates<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>(`self.ptr`)<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`selection_template`<sp/>object,<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>lifecycle<sp/>and<sp/>exposing<sp/>its<sp/>parameters<sp/>and<sp/>functionalities<sp/>as<sp/>Python<sp/>properties<sp/>and<sp/>methods.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
