<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer.<sp/>If<sp/>`inpt`<sp/>(a<sp/>dictionary)<sp/>is<sp/>provided,<sp/>it<sp/>attempts<sp/>to<sp/>set<sp/>various<sp/>attributes<sp/>of<sp/>`self`<sp/>from<sp/>`inpt[&quot;data&quot;]`.<sp/>It<sp/>also<sp/>initializes<sp/>`self.ptr.passed_weights`<sp/>and<sp/>`self.ptr.matched_meta`<sp/>from<sp/>`inpt[&quot;weights&quot;]`<sp/>and<sp/>`inpt[&quot;meta&quot;]`<sp/>respectively,<sp/>converting<sp/>them<sp/>from<sp/>Python<sp/>types<sp/>to<sp/>C++<sp/>maps.</highlight></codeline>
